# Resume ATS Compatibility Analyzer

## Overview
Resume ATS Compatibility Analyzer is a web application designed to help job seekers evaluate their resumes against Applicant Tracking Systems (ATS). This tool analyzes the content of a resume and provides a score based on various criteria, helping users optimize their resumes for better chances of passing through ATS filters.

## Features
- User-friendly interface for resume input.
- Real-time ATS score calculation.
- Responsive design using Bootstrap.
- Custom styling for enhanced user experience.

## Project Structure
```
ats-score-generator
├── src
│   ├── index.html         # Main HTML document
│   ├── css
│   │   └── styles.css     # Custom styles
│   ├── js
│   │   └── app.js         # JavaScript functionality
│   └── assets             # Directory for additional assets
└── README.md              # Project documentation
```

## Installation
1. Clone the repository:
   ```
   git clone <repository-url>
   ```
2. Navigate to the project directory:
   ```
   cd ats-score-generator
   ```
3. Open the `src/index.html` file in your web browser to view the application.

## Usage
- Input your resume content into the provided text area.
- Click the "Calculate Score" button to receive your ATS score.
- Review the suggestions provided to improve your resume.

